Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅澤！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追的話得趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說什麼皇家什麼教會的時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有理由！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑟爾蓋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格魯德曼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷 這樣下去德澤爾會被污穢纏身的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德澤爾這邊我們會想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷去找羅澤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等出事就晚了 你趕快做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:44.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しみに囚われた魂達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:44.54,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}為悲傷所困的靈魂們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:54.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}終わらない憎しみが叫びだす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:54.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}因無盡的憎恨而呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:59.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}迷いの森を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:59.63,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}穿過迷惘的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界照らしに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們將去照亮世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:08.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絶望抱きしめるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:08.70,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}會去擁抱絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:13.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}諦めていない証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:13.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}說明還未放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:19.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}孤独超えたら信じあえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:19.30,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}當我們跨越孤獨便可互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絆離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要放開這份情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:26.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望という眩しい重さに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:26.99,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望炫目而又沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:32.69,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}負けない情熱この手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:32.69,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中握有不被壓倒的熱誠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:39.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想い  光へ  何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:39.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}思念化作光芒 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}命尽き果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.19,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至生命耗盡
